Package: rawrr
Title: A Reddit API Wrapper for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "andrés",
           family = "castro araújo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "acastroaraujo@gmai.com")
Description: This package calls a limited subset of Reddit's API in order to gather 
  information on threads, subreddits, and users. It calls Python's PRAW library via 
  the reticulate package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
